ascend_skill.desc:
When taking damage from a foe's skill, 65% chance to activate Resonance and counterattack, dealing Ice damage equal to 88% of Yusuke's Defense.
Evolve this effect to Imagination by using a skill.
ascend_skill.name: Inspiration

ascend_skill.desc: Every 2 times Keen Eye is used, activate Imagination 1 time as a follow-up. Counterattacks activated by this effect deal 70% of the original damage.
ascend_skill.name: Natural Talent

ascend_skill.desc: When Yusuke's HP is above 70%, increase counterattack damage dealt to foes by 35%.
ascend_skill.name: Both Beauty and Vice

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Keen Eye and Thief Tactics by 3.
ascend_skill.name: A Breathtaking Sight

ascend_skill.desc: Highlight Enhanced: After using a Highlight, increase counterattack damage by 30% for 3 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Still Life

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Frozen Presence and Bone-Chilling Cold by 3.
ascend_skill.name: With a Single Stroke

ascend_skill.desc:
Evolve the effects of Inspiration and Imagination to Vision & Emotion and Creation.
Each counterattack becomes 2 consecutive attacks, each dealing 90% of the original attack's damage. Also increase counterattack pierce rate by 30%.
ascend_skill.name: Finishing Touches

highlight_skill.desc: Deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 178.1%/196.4%/189.1%/207.3% of Yusuke's Defense. Increase chance of activating Inspiration counterattacks by 35% for 3 turns.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc: Deal Ice damage to all foes equal to 72.1%/79.5%/76.6%/84.0% of Yusuke's Defense. Inflict Freeze on main target for 2 turns.
normal_skill.name: Frozen Presence

normal_skill.desc: Deal Ice damage to foes equal to 92.9%/102.4%/98.6%/108.1% of Yusuke's Defense (5 hits). When Yusuke has a shield, increase damage by 30%. From the second hit, prioritize new targets and decrease damage by 60% for each hit on the same target (max decrease to 20% of Defense).
normal_skill.name: Bone-Chilling Cold

normal_skill.desc:
Evolve the next activated Inspiration to Imagination. 
Imagination: Increase chance of counterattack to 100%, increase damage by 78.1%/86.1%/82.9%/90.9% of Defense, and change target to all foes. If the effect is not activated by the start of Yusuke's next action, automatically activate it.
For 2 turns, gain a shield equal to 19.5%/19.5%/20.7%/20.7% of Yusuke's Defense + 555/555/683/683, increase Fire resistance, and nullify spiritual ailments.
Also inflict Taunt on all foes for 2 turns.
Cooldown Time: 1 turn.
normal_skill.name: Keen Eye

passive_skill.desc: Each time a shield is gained, increase damage dealt to foes by 7.5% for 2 turns. Stacks up to 6 times.
passive_skill.name: Painter's Focus

passive_skill.desc: Each time a shield is gained with Yusuke's skills, increase Yusuke's pierce rate by 20.0% for 1 turn.
passive_skill.name: Artist's Intuition
